data.description: Impressive New Price on this spacious 5 bedroom home on an acre lot located in the award winning Mandeville school district. 1 year old roof.  This move-in ready home has a fantastic floor plan with high ceilings, crown moldings and plantation shutters. The formal dining room open to the living room with wood flooring and fireplace. Chef's kitchen with lots of cabinets, granite counters, island, gas cooking with a keeping room. Beautiful nature views from the keeping room of the backyard and woodland beyond. Covered patio.  Private owner's suite with luxury bath and XL closet. Guest suite split from other bedrooms. Big laundry/mud room with cubbies for all your gear. Long double driveway can fit many cars. Double attached garage. American Home Shield Warranty included in the Sale  This home is built on a ridge overlooking the woodlands beyond, a tranquil and private setting with no backyard neighbors.  Convenient to the Causeway Bridge, Mandeville schools & shopping or the charming town of Madisonville and Tchefuncte River. It's also just a short bike ride to Franco's athletic club on the bike path by Penn's Chapel. Steeple Place is a beautiful, serene, small cul-de-sac neighborhood in Mandeville, truly a hidden treasure.
